**Addendum:** Following the prior event, a request was pushed from research staff to rewrite containment protocol of SCP-8619 with respect to new findings. This request has been ##red|Denied,## as under current circumstances, it is immeasurably unlikely that any human being will reach their full evolutionary potential in the wild.


